RBEI/BE-BS offers business IT solutions in the areas of engineering, manufacturing, automation and infrastructure services with a view to leveraging both our business and technical expertise in providing innovative solutions to our customer needs. With a focus on agility, scalability, productivity, and the ability to deliver at optimum costs, BE-BS is organized as Enterprise Core, Enterprise Applications, Enterprise Platforms, Engineering Tools, Mechanical Engineering, and Business Services to foster value and build trusted partnerships with customers.

The services portfolio comprises business consulting and end-to-end solutions including implementation, maintenance and support for the following services:
ERP services
Product Lifecycle Management (PLM)
IT application development
Automation solutions
IT infrastructure
Engineering tools
Mechanical engineering
User Experience (UX)
Business Excellence
PMO Services
